    </ul>
   </div>
 </section>
 
  <!--ADD TO CART--> 
  <%- include("./partials/cart.ejs") %>
  
      <section id="prodetails" class="section-p1">
        <div class="single-pro-image">
          <img src="/img/project/scarf/scarf1.jpg" width="100%" id="MainImg">
          <div class="small-img-group">
            <div class="small-img-col">
              <img src="/img/project/scarf/scarf1.jpg" width="100%" height="80%" class="small-img">
            </div>
            <div class="small-img-col">
              <img src="/img/project/scarf/scarf2.1.jpg" width="100%" height="80%" class="small-img">
            </div>
            <div class="small-img-col">
              <img src="/img/project/scarf/scarf3.jpg" width="100%" height="80%" class="small-img">
            </div>
            <div class="small-img-col">
              <img src="/img/project/scarf/scarf4.2.jpg" width="100%" height="80%" class="small-img">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
    
      <div class="single-pro-details">
        <h6>Handcrafted</h6>
        <h2><%= result.Name %></h4>
        <h4>Rs.<%= result.Price %></h2>
        <h6>In stock:<%= result.NumberOf %></h6>
        <form method="post" action="/add_cartp">
          <input type="number" value="1" min="0" max=<%= result.NumberOf %> name="item_count">
          <input type="hidden" name="Id" value=<%= result.Id %>>
          <input type="hidden" name="Name" value=<%= result.Name %>>
          <input type="hidden" name="Price" value="<%= result.Price %>">
          <input type="hidden" name="Link" value=<%= result.Link %>>
          <input type="submit" style="width: 200px;" class="addCart" value="Add to Cart">
      </form>
        <h4>Product Details</h4>
        <span><%= result.Description %></span>
      </div>
    </section>
      <section class="person" style="display: flex;">
        <div>
          <img src="/img/project/scarf/person4.jpg"></div>
          <div><p class="person-details">
            From the heart of rural India, resides Amrita, a venerable woman whose nimble fingers dance with threads of tradition. With a weathered loom as her companion, she weaves intricate scarves, each strand telling a story of resilience and heritage. Guided by the whispers of her ancestors, Amrita's hands move with a rhythmic grace, blending colors and patterns passed down through generations. As the loom sings its ancient melody, Amrita's spirit soars, infusing each scarf with the warmth of her love and the wisdom of her years. Through her craft, she not only creates garments but also preserves the rich tapestry of Indian culture, reminding us of the beauty found in age-old traditions and the timeless artistry of the human touch.
          </p></div>
      </section>
      <script>
        var MainImg = document.getElementById("MainImg");
        var smallimg = document.getElementsByClassName("small-img");
    
        smallimg[0].onclick = function () {
          MainImg.src = smallimg[0].src;
        }
        smallimg[1].onclick = function () {
          MainImg.src = smallimg[1].src;
        }
        smallimg[2].onclick = function () {
          MainImg.src = smallimg[2].src;
        }
        smallimg[3].onclick = function () {
          MainImg.src = smallimg[3].src;
        }
      </script>
